{"id": 231931362, "title": "Reiss\u2019 twisted secret exposed as legend stumbles upon the truth", "text": "Reiss has made a huge mistake (Picture: BBC/Jack Barnes/Kieron McCarron) Reiss Colwell\u2019s (Jonny Freeman) big secret is set to be exposed by Bianca Jackson (Patsy Palmer) next week. The two have come to blows recently, with Reiss fretting about being able to financially support his family once Sonia Fowler (Natalie Cassidy) gives birth, and Bianca believing her own issues with adoptive daughter Whitney Dean (Shona McGarty) to be more important. Reiss had lost one of his most valued clients, and Kathy Beale (Gillian Taylforth) suggested he speak with Phil Mitchell (Steve McFadden), who was looking for an accountant. When it was revealed that Sonia actually had a blighted ovum and was never pregnant, the couple were left devastated. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that supports HTML5 video Up Next Bianca\u2019s got her eye on him (Picture: BBC/Jack Barnes/Kieron McCarron) Next week, tensions to continue within the household as his financial situation worsens and Sonia suggests trying IVF again. In a shocking act of desperation, Reiss hopes Kat Mitchell (Jessie Wallace) can cough up some cash and tells her that her tax bill is overdue. The blatant lie leaves him riddled with guilt. Bianca becomes suspicious when Jay Brown (Jamie Borthwick) reveals that Reiss tried to sell his car to him, and with Kat also confused over his claims, she follows him to the care home where he is visiting his wife Debbie. Will she do the right thing and tell her sister? (Picture: BBC/Jack Barnes/Kieron McCarron) Follow Metro Soaps on WhatsApp and get all the latest spoilers first! Want to be the first to hear shocking EastEnders spoilers? Who\u2019s leaving Coronation Street? The latest gossip from Emmerdale? Join 10,000 soaps fans on Metro's WhatsApp Soaps community and get access to spoiler galleries, must-watch videos, and exclusive interviews. Simply click on this link, select \u2018Join Chat\u2019 and you\u2019re in! Don't forget to turn on notifications so you can see when we've just dropped the latest spoilers! As viewers of the BBC One soap will know, Debbie has been in a coma since suffering a stroke in the bath, and in shocking scenes he used her money to pay for the initial IVF treatment. During his visit to his wife, Reiss asks her for permission to borrow more money, but is taken aback when Bianca appears from the shadows. Disgusted by his behaviour, Bianca offers him an ultimatum \u2013 tell her sister everything, or she will. Could this spell an end for Sonia and Reiss, and Bianca\u2019s time in Walford? If you\u2019ve got a soap or TV story, video or pictures get in touch by emailing us soaps@metro.co.uk \u2013 we\u2019d love to hear from you. Join the community by leaving a comment below and stay updated on all things soaps on our homepage.", "summary": "A shocking act of desperation.", "url": "https://metro.co.uk/2024/06/09/reiss-twisted-secret-exposed-legend-stumbles-upon-truth-20968424/", "image": "https://metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/478352-5dfe.jpg?quality=90&strip=all", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 12:00:00", "author": "Michael Adams", "authors": ["Michael Adams"], "language": "en", "source_country": "gb", "sentiment": -0.287}